{"tid":1054583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"露宿男倒斃通州街公園　遺體舁送殮房途中再遇車禍","createTime":"2019-03-10T02:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T04:51:40.000Z","uid":41404,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d25f6095c7afe8e016b59b70548c0fcdfd8c30d0","tid":1054583,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:18:43.000Z","msg":"深水埗通州街163號通州街公園，今早(10日)6時32分，一名50餘歲男子被發現昏迷小食亭附近，救護員接報到場，證實男子已氣絕身亡。警方到場調查，在現場發現水樽及紙巾等個人物品，相信死者在上址露宿，初步相信案件無可疑，惟死因有待剖驗，正設法聯絡其家人助查。 <br />\n<br />\n至早上8時09分，死者的遺體由黑箱車舁走殮房途中，現場下着大雨，當駛至旺角道近上海街交界時，黑箱車疑在燈位前收掣不及，撞向前面一輛外賣電單車，以致南亞裔鐵騎士墮地，手腳受傷。救護員接報到場，為傷者包紮後送院，黑箱車上的司機及仵工俱無恙，警方正調查意外原因。至於死者的遺體則由另一輛黑箱車到場舁走，繼續行程。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190310/mobile/bkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190310%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001.html&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2MbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=70f4bda1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190310/mobile/bkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5c9b33a4fd67bfe85828aeff2cf365695ec752d7","tid":1054583,"uid":51620,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慘"},{"pid":"8bd0df0a06527ad0f9a9af5e70c49f2bd890dc9b","tid":1054583,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"佢都有阿媽生架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73f2c46182c97f4bcd8245f3d8ac130c7a4b504","tid":1054583,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"這就是香港.jpg"},{"pid":"48669749cdb276b685b57e43d58b5cc0e15556fa","tid":1054583,"uid":162274,"like":3,"dislik